{"type":"message","id":"936d424d","parentId":"98017ad7","timestamp":"2026-06-12T03:17:59.058Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在逐一修复问题：\n\n**问题分析：**\n\n1. **CMD弹窗** - 可能是 WASM SDK 的 `I_InitPlugin` 或某些命令执行\n2. **PTZ/OSD开关报错** - 按钮 ID 不匹配：HTML 中是 `btnPtzOsd`，但 JS 中调用了 `btnPtzOsdOn`/`btnPtzOsdOff`\n3. **白平衡自动模式滑动条问题** - 拉动滑动条立刻变自动，且无法再调试\n4. **光圈、快门无法设置** - 需要检查 API 调用逻辑\n5. **饱和度、亮度滑动条右侧需显示数值** - 需添加显示元素\n\n开始修复：\n\n**修复 #2：PTZ/OSD 开关按钮 ID 不匹配问题**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-e24a6fad04fe44c99d18584f5b35c92e","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"// PTZ 坐标显示开关\n        function togglePtzOsd(enabled) {\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n            if (!dev) { showToast('warning', '请先选择设备'); return; }\n            // 更新按钮状态（v5.46: 使用正确的按钮 ID）\n            window.updatePtzOsdButtons(enabled);\n            apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/osd/ptz', { enabled: enabled }).then(function(result) {\n                if (result && result.success) {\n                    showToast('success', result.message || 'PTZ OSD: ' + (enabled ? '显示' : '关闭'));\n                } else {\n                    showToast('error', result ? result.message : 'PTZ OSD 切换失败');\n                }\n            }).catch(function(e) { showToast('error', 'PTZ OSD 切换异常: ' + e.message); });\n        }","oldText":"// PTZ 坐标显示开关\n        function togglePtzOsd(enabled) {\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n            if (!dev) { showToast('warning', '请先选择设备'); return; }\n            apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/osd/ptz?enabled=' + enabled, null).then(function(result) {\n                if (result && result.success) {\n                    showToast('success', result.message);\n                    document.getElementById('btnPtzOsdOn').className = enabled ? 'btn btn-sm btn-primary' : 'btn btn-sm btn-secondary';\n                    document.getElementById('btnPtzOsdOff').className = enabled ? 'btn btn-sm btn-secondary' : 'btn btn-sm btn-primary';\n                } else {\n                    showToast('error', result ? result.message : 'PTZ OSD 切换失败');\n                }\n            }).catch(function(e) { showToast('error', 'PTZ OSD 切换异常: ' + e.message); });\n        }"},{"newText":"// OSD 信息显示开关（用户自定义、日期时间等）\n        function toggleInfoOsd(enabled) {\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n            if (!dev) { showToast('warning', '请先选择设备'); return; }\n            // 更新按钮状态（v5.46: 使用正确的按钮 ID）\n            window.updateInfoOsdButtons(enabled);\n            apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/osd/info', { enabled: enabled }).then(function(result) {\n                if (result && result.success) {\n                    showToast('success', result.message || 'Info OSD: ' + (enabled ? '显示' : '关闭'));\n                } else {\n                    showToast('error', result ? result.message : 'OSD 切换失败');\n                }\n            }).catch(function(e) { showToast('error', 'OSD 切换异常: ' + e.message); });\n        }","oldText":"// OSD 信息显示开关（用户自定义、日期时间等）\n        function toggleInfoOsd(enabled) {\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n            if (!dev) { showToast('warning', '请先选择设备'); return; }\n            apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/osd/info?enabled=' + enabled, null).then(function(result) {\n                if (result && result.success) {\n                    showToast('success', result.message);\n                    document.getElementById('btnInfoOsdOn').className = enabled ? 'btn btn-sm btn-primary' : 'btn btn-sm btn-secondary';\n                    document.getElementById('btnInfoOsdOff').className = enabled ? 'btn btn-sm btn-secondary' : 'btn btn-sm btn-primary';\n                } else {\n                    showToast('error', result ? result.message : 'OSD 切换失败');\n                }\n            }).catch(function(e) { showToast('error', 'OSD 切换异常: ' + e.message); });\n        }"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":54254,"output":1130,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55384,"cost":{"input":0.054254,"output":0.0036160000000000003,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.05787}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781234251787,"responseId":"cht000d56c1@dx19eb9d5bac3b894142"}}
