{"type":"message","id":"320df555","parentId":"5376ded9","timestamp":"2026-06-12T03:25:08.805Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_8e01ac02cf3044a9af039604","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n    client = ctrl.client\r\n    try:\r\n        level = data.get(\"level\", \"1/60\")\r\n        \r\n        xml_str = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n<Shutter version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\r\n  <ShutterLevel>{level}</ShutterLevel>\r\n</Shutter>'''\r\n\r\n        put_resp = client.put(\"/Image/channels/1/Shutter\", xml_str)\r\n        if put_resp.status_code == 200:\r\n            return {\"success\": True, \"message\": f\"快门已设置为 {level}\"}\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"更新失败: HTTP {put_resp.status_code}\"}\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"设置快门异常: {e}\"}\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/iris\", summary=\"获取光圈设置\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def get_iris(device_id: str) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"获取设备光圈当前设置。\"\"\"\r\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n    mgr: PTZManager | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_manager\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZManager 未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n\r\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n    client = ctrl.client\r\n    try:\r\n        resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/Iris\")\r\n        if resp.status_code != 200:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"获取光圈失败: HTTP {resp.status_code}\"}\r\n\r\n        root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\r\n        result = {\"success\": True, \"data\": {}}\r\n        for elem in root.iter():\r\n            tag = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\r\n            if tag in (\"IrisLevel\", \"irisLevel\"):\r\n                result[\"data\"][\"current_level\"] = int((elem.text or \"160\").strip())\r\n            elif tag in (\"minIrisLevelLimit\", \"MinIrisLevelLimit\"):\r\n                result[\"data\"][\"min\"] = int((elem.text or \"160\").strip())\r\n            elif tag in (\"maxIrisLevelLimit\", \"MaxIrisLevelLimit\"):\r\n                result[\"data\"][\"max\"] = int((elem.text or \"2200\").strip())\r\n\r\n        return result\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"获取光圈异常: {e}\"}\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.post(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/iris\", summary=\"设置光圈\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def set_iris(device_id: str, data: dict) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"设置光圈参数。\"\"\"\r\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n    mgr: PTZManager | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_manager\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZManager 未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n\r\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n    client = ctrl.client\r\n    try:\r\n        level = data.get(\"level\", 160)\r\n        \r\n        xml_str = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n<Iris version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\r\n  <IrisLevel>{level}</IrisLevel>\r\n</Iris>'''\r\n\r\n        put_resp = client.put(\"/Image/channels/1/Iris\", xml_str)\r\n        if put_resp.status_code == 200:\r\n            return {\"success\": True, \"message\": f\"光圈已设置\"}\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"更新失败: HTTP {put_resp.status_code}\"}\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"设置光圈异常: {e}\"}\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/sharpness\", summary=\"获取锐度设置\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def get_sharpness(device_id: str) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"获取设备锐度当前设置。\"\"\"\r\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n    mgr: PTZManager | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_manager\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZManager 未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n\n[171 more lines in file. Use offset=2868 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781234708805}}
{"type":"message","id":"e48090f8","parentId":"320df555","timestamp":"2026-06-12T03:25:21.704Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"后端 API 看起来正确。问题可能是：\n1. 快门/光圈端点需要先关闭自动模式\n2. 需要检查设备实际支持的端点\n\n让我检查前端的快门和光圈设置逻辑是否需要改进。先检查快门设置函数："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_80ddaa3c06c74052b67a5f39","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":750,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":87248,"output":108,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87356,"cost":{"input":0.08724799999999999,"output":0.00034560000000000005,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0875936}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781234708806,"responseId":"cht000d9f97@dx19eb9dcc625b8ab282"}}
{"type":"message","id":"85068ff7","parentId":"e48090f8","timestamp":"2026-06-12T03:25:21.712Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_80ddaa3c06c74052b67a5f39","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"function setNoiseReduce(type, value) {\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n    if (!dev) return;\n    \n    // 更新显示\n    var el = document.getElementById(type === 'spatial' ? 'dnrSpatialVal' : 'dnrTemporalVal');\n    if (el) el.textContent = value;\n    \n    // 发送请求\n    var key = type === 'spatial' ? 'spatial_level' : 'temporal_level';\n    apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/noisereduce', { [key]: parseInt(value) });\n}\n\n// 设置快门\nfunction setShutterSpeed(value) {\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n    if (!dev) return;\n    \n    if (value === 'auto') {\n        apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/shutter', { mode: 'auto' });\n    } else {\n        apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/shutter', { level: value })\n            .then(function(r) {\n                if (r && r.success) showToast('success', '快门: ' + value);\n            });\n    }\n}\n\n// 设置光圈\nfunction setIris(value) {\n\n[98 more lines in file. Use offset=780 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781234721712}}
{"type":"message","id":"0fa65416","parentId":"85068ff7","timestamp":"2026-06-12T03:25:44.647Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"前端代码看起来正确。问题可能在于：\n1. 快门需要在特定模式下才能设置（如手动曝光模式）\n2. 光圈需要在手动光圈模式下才能设置\n\n这需要在后端添加曝光模式和光圈模式的设置。但老板要求\"禁止过度开发\"，我只报告这个问题：\n\n**汇总修复完成情况：**\n\n| # | 问题 | 状态 | 修复内容 |\n|---|------|------|----------|\n| 1 | CMD 弹窗 | ✅ 已修复 | 添加 `CREATE_NO_WINDOW` 到 FFmpeg/PING/ASTAP subprocess 调用 |\n| 2 | PTZ/OSD 开关报错 | ✅ 已修复 | 按钮ID不匹配，使用正确的 `btnPtzOsd`/`btnInfoOsd` |\n| 3 | 白平衡滑动条问题 | ✅ 已修复 | 拉动前先切换到手动模式，并启用滑动条 |\n| 4 | 光圈、快门无法设置 | ⚠️ 需验证 | API 端点正确，可能需要设备切换曝光模式 |\n| 5 | 滑动条显示数值 | ✅ 已修复 | 添加 `oninput` 更新数值显示，压缩间距 |\n\n让我更新 HEARTBEAT.md："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_79f5427c2d7e431a96bb0b1e","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 心跳与任务状态\n\n**最后更新**: 2026-06-12 11:30\n**状态**: v5.46 细节修复\n**工作空间**: C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\n\n### v5.46 修复内容\n| # | 问题 | 状态 | 修复内容 |\n|---|------|------|----------|\n| 1 | CMD 弹窗 | ✅ 已修复 | FFmpeg/PING/ASTAP subprocess 添加 CREATE_NO_WINDOW |\n| 2 | PTZ/OSD 开关报错 | ✅ 已修复 | 按钮 ID 不匹配，使用正确的 updatePtzOsdButtons |\n| 3 | 白平衡滑动条 | ✅ 已修复 | 拉动前切换手动模式，启用滑动条 |\n| 4 | 光圈、快门无法设置 | ⚠️ 需验证 | API 正确，可能需设备切换曝光模式 |\n| 5 | 滑动条显示数值 | ✅ 已修复 | 添加 oninput 更新数值，压缩间距 |\n\n### 技术教训\n1. Windows subprocess 调用必须添加 `CREATE_NO_WINDOW` 防止 CMD 弹窗\n2. HTML 按钮和 JS 函数的 ID 必须一致\n3. 白平衡增益调整需要先切换到手动模式\n\n### 正确端口\n- **AstroHub**: 10280\n- **摄像头 ISAPI**: 80\n- **摄像头 WebSocket**: 7681\n","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":87698,"output":636,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88334,"cost":{"input":0.087698,"output":0.0020352,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0897332}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781234721714,"responseId":"cht000d912e@dx19eb9dceb54ba5a412"}}
