{"type":"message","id":"1c8a0c40","parentId":"ff61399a","timestamp":"2026-06-12T03:31:26.977Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"海康 ISAPI 文档说明：\n- **快门和光圈需要在手动曝光模式下才能设置**\n- **曝光模式端点**: `/Image/channels/1/exposure` 或 `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/exposure`\n\n让我检查海康 ISAPI 标准文档格式。基于我的知识：\n\n**海康 ISAPI 曝光模式设置：**\n\n```\n端点: PUT /ISAPI/Image/channels/1/exposure\nXML:\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<Exposure version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\n  <ExposureMode>manual</ExposureMode>  <!-- 或 auto, shutter-priority, iris-priority -->\n</Exposure>\n```\n\n**曝光模式选项：**\n- `auto` - 自动曝光（快门和光圈都自动）\n- `manual` - 手动曝光（快门和光圈都手动）\n- `shutter-priority` - 快门优先（快门手动，光圈自动）\n- `iris-priority` - 光圈优先（光圈手动，快门自动）\n\n所以问题的根因是：**当前设备可能在 `auto` 模式下，无法设置快门和光圈。**\n\n我需要在设置快门/光圈前先切换曝光模式。让我添加曝光模式切换功能："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-a70d74af1cff4606953cc4dcbfed3593","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"@api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/exposure\", summary=\"获取曝光模式\", tags=[\"Image\"])\nasync def get_exposure(device_id: str) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"获取设备曝光当前模式。\"\"\"\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n    mgr: PTZManager | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_manager\")\n    if not mgr:\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZManager 未初始化\"}\n\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\n    if not target_ip:\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\n\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\n    if err:\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\n\n    client = ctrl.client\n    try:\n        resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/exposure\")\n        if resp.status_code != 200:\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"获取曝光模式失败: HTTP {resp.status_code}\"}\n\n        root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\n        result = {\"success\": True, \"data\": {}}\n        for elem in root.iter():\n            tag = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\n            if tag in (\"ExposureMode\", \"exposureMode\"):\n                result[\"data\"][\"mode\"] = elem.text or \"auto\"\n\n        # 如果没有找到曝光模式，默认 auto\n        if \"mode\" not in result[\"data\"]:\n            result[\"data\"][\"mode\"] = \"auto\"\n        return result\n    except Exception as e:\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"获取曝光模式异常: {e}\"}\n\n\n@api_router.post(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/exposure\", summary=\"设置曝光模式\", tags=[\"Image\"])\nasync def set_exposure(device_id: str, data: dict) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"设置曝光模式。\"\"\"\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n    mgr: PTZManager | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_manager\")\n    if not mgr:\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZManager 未初始化\"}\n\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\n    if not target_ip:\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\n\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\n    if err:\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\n\n    client = ctrl.client\n    try:\n        mode = data.get(\"mode\", \"manual\")\n        # mode: auto, manual, shutter-priority, iris-priority\n        \n        xml_str = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<Exposure version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\n  <ExposureMode>{mode}</ExposureMode>\n</Exposure>'''\n\n        put_resp = client.put(\"/Image/channels/1/exposure\", xml_str)\n        if put_resp.status_code == 200:\n            return {\"success\": True, \"message\": f\"曝光模式已设置为 {mode}\"}\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"更新失败: HTTP {put_resp.status_code}\"}\n    except Exception as e:\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"设置曝光模式异常: {e}\"}\n\n\n@api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/shutter\", summary=\"获取快门设置\", tags=[\"Image\"])","oldText":"@api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/shutter\", summary=\"获取快门设置\", tags=[\"Image\"])"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":91985,"output":1243,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93228,"cost":{"input":0.091985,"output":0.0039776,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0959626}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781235051842,"responseId":"cht000dd756@dx19eb9e1f0edb894142"}}
