{"type":"message","id":"527f0b03","parentId":"0d334d63","timestamp":"2026-06-12T03:32:55.658Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"更新 HEARTBEAT："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-28d1fcc07a3f4c3e9d3fe45ca4741c81","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 心跳与任务状态\n\n**最后更新**: 2026-06-12 11:45\n**状态**: v5.46 细节修复完成\n**工作空间**: C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\n\n### v5.46 修复内容\n| # | 问题 | 状态 | 修复内容 |\n|---|------|------|----------|\n| 1 | CMD 弹窗 | ✅ 已修复 | FFmpeg/PING/ASTAP subprocess 添加 CREATE_NO_WINDOW |\n| 2 | PTZ/OSD 开关报错 | ✅ 已修复 | 按钮 ID 不匹配，使用正确的 updatePtzOsdButtons |\n| 3 | 白平衡滑动条 | ✅ 已修复 | 拉动前切换手动模式，启用滑动条 |\n| 4 | 光圈、快门无法设置 | ✅ 已修复 | 添加曝光模式切换，设置前切换到对应优先模式 |\n| 5 | 滑动条显示数值 | ✅ 已修复 | 添加 oninput 更新数值，压缩间距 |\n\n### 海康 ISAPI 曝光模式配置\n```\n端点: PUT /Image/channels/1/exposure\n模式: auto | manual | shutter-priority | iris-priority\n\n- auto: 自动曝光（快门和光圈都自动）\n- manual: 手动曝光（快门和光圈都手动）\n- shutter-priority: 快门优先（快门手动，光圈自动）\n- iris-priority: 光圈优先（光圈手动，快门自动）\n```\n\n### 技术教训\n1. Windows subprocess 调用必须添加 CREATE_NO_WINDOW 防止 CMD 弹窗\n2. HTML 按钮和 JS 函数的 ID 必须一致\n3. 白平衡增益调整需要先切换到手动模式\n4. 海康摄像头快门/光圈设置需要先切换曝光模式\n\n### 正确端口\n- **AstroHub**: 10280\n- **摄像头 ISAPI**: 80\n- **摄像头 WebSocket**: 7681","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":95268,"output":489,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":95757,"cost":{"input":0.09526799999999999,"output":0.0015648,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0968328}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781235152510,"responseId":"cht000de4eb@dx19eb9e38b10b85e102"}}
