{"type":"message","id":"165d0182","parentId":"16c12072","timestamp":"2026-06-12T08:02:59.908Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Step 2：添加获取已连接设备状态 API**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d5bc89e305fc4f2682e9f21f","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":1595,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\core\\ptz_manager.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":150077,"output":60,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":150137,"cost":{"input":0.150077,"output":0.000192,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.15026899999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781251346304,"responseId":"cht000dfdb5@dx19ebadae8efba5a412"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0d499007","parentId":"165d0182","timestamp":"2026-06-12T08:02:59.919Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d5bc89e305fc4f2682e9f21f","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\r\n    def list_controllers(self) -> list[str]:\r\n        return list(self._controllers.keys())\r\n\r\n    def is_device_connected(self, ip: str) -> bool:\r\n        return ip in self._controllers\r\n\r\n    # ================================================================\r\n    #  设备信息获取\r\n    # ================================================================\r\n\r\n    def get_device_info(self, ip: str) -> dict:\r\n        \"\"\"通过 ISAPI 获取设备详细信息。\"\"\"\r\n        if ip not in self._clients:\r\n            # 尝试自动连接\r\n            creds = self.get_credentials(ip)\r\n            if creds:\r\n                client = ISAPIClient(ip=ip, username=creds[\"username\"],\r\n                                     password=creds[\"password\"], port=creds.get(\"port\", 80))\r\n                if not client.verify_credentials():\r\n                    return {\"error\": \"认证失败\"}\r\n                self._clients[ip] = client\r\n                self._controllers[ip] = PTZController(client)\r\n            else:\r\n                return {\"error\": \"设备未连接且无凭据\"}\r\n\r\n        client = self._clients[ip]\r\n        info = {}\r\n\r\n        # 系统信息\r\n        result = client.get(\"/System/deviceInfo\")\r\n        if result.status_code == 200:\r\n            try:\r\n                root = ET.fromstring(result.xml)\r\n                info[\"device_name\"] = client.get_xml_text(root, \"deviceName\", \"\")\r\n                info[\"model\"] = client.get_xml_text(root, \"model\", \"\")\r\n                info[\"serial_number\"] = client.get_xml_text(root, \"serialNumber\", \"\")\r\n                info[\"firmware_version\"] = client.get_xml_text(root, \"firmwareVersion\", \"\")\r\n                info[\"mac_address\"] = client.get_xml_text(root, \"macAddress\", \"\")\r\n            except Exception as e:\r\n                LOG.log(\"warning\", f\"解析设备信息异常: {e}\")\r\n\r\n        # 网络配置\r\n        net_result = client.get(\"/Network/interfaces/1\")\r\n        if net_result.status_code == 200:\r\n            try:\r\n                root = ET.fromstring(net_result.xml)\r\n                info[\"network\"] = {\r\n                    \"ip\": client.get_xml_text(root, \"ipAddress\", \"\"),\r\n                    \"subnet_mask\": client.get_xml_text(root, \"subnetMask\", \"\"),\r\n\n[1087 more lines in file. Use offset=1645 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781251379919}}
{"type":"compaction","id":"e86059ff","parentId":"0d499007","timestamp":"2026-06-12T08:04:21.833Z","summary":"## Goal\n用户要求修复 AstroHub v5.46 的 5 个细节问题：CMD 弹窗、PTZ/OSD 开关报错、白平衡滑动条问题、光圈/快门无法设置、滑动条显示数值。\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- 禁止过度开发，针对性修复\n- 备份后更新\n- 当前版本需从 v5.45 升级到 v5.46\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] CMD 弹窗修复：在 `ptz_manager.py` (FFmpeg/PING) 和 `astap_solve.py` (ASTAP) 的 subprocess 调用中添加 `creationflags=subprocess.CREATE_NO_WINDOW`\n- [x] PTZ/OSD 开关报错修复：`index.html` 中 `togglePtzOsd`/`toggleInfoOsd` 函数使用正确的按钮 ID 和 `window.updatePtzOsdButtons`/`window.updateInfoOsdButtons`\n- [x] 白平衡滑动条问题修复：`console.html` 中 `setWhiteBalanceGain` 函数在拉动前先切换到手动模式并启用滑动条\n- [x] 滑动条显示数值修复：亮度/对比度/饱和度/锐度/降噪等滑动条添加 `oninput` 实时更新数值显示，压缩行间距（margin-bottom: 4px）\n- [x] 版本号更新：`index.html` 中版本从 v5.45 改为 v5.46\n- [x] 备份创建：`backup_20260612_105500/`\n- [x] 光圈/快门无法设置问题修复：添加曝光模式切换功能，设置快门/光圈前自动切换到对应优先模式\n\n### In Progress\n- 无（v5.46 所有修复已完成）\n\n### Blocked\n- 无\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **CMD 弹窗**：Windows subprocess 必须使用 `CREATE_NO_WINDOW` 防止控制台窗口闪现\n- **白平衡增益**：调整前必须先切换到手动模式，否则\n\n[Compaction summary truncated to fit budget]\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Goal\n修改 AstroHub v5.48 版本，进行精确修复：\n1. SADP 发现只在程序启动时运行一次，点击刷新按钮时再运行（而非点击标签就刷新）\n2. 从本地配置文件读取记录，记忆之前的连接，启动程序默认是断开状态\n3. 移除 ptzvflow 和 nic selector 功能\n4. 检测系统信息使用之前记录的 ptz start up 脚本\n5. 禁止使用 cmd 方式打开脚本（astrohub 是面向多端多平台的 portable 程序）\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- 禁止过度开发\n- astrohub 是面向多端多平台的 portable 程序\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] 创建备份目录 `backup_20260612_154300`\n- [x] 备份 `src/web/index.html`\n- [x] 备份 `src/main.py`\n- [x] 备份 `src/core/ptz_manager.py`\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] 修复 SADP 发现逻辑（只在启动和手动刷新时运行）\n- [ ] 移除 ptzvflow 和 nic selector 功能\n- [ ] 禁止使用 cmd 方式打开脚本\n\n### Blocked\n- 无\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **备份策略**: 在修改前先备份关键文件到 `backup_20260612_154300` 目录\n\n## Next Steps\n1. 修改 index.html 中的 SADP 发现逻辑，移除标签点击时的 autoSadpDiscover() 调用\n2. 移除 ptzvflow 和 nic selector 相关代码\n3. 修改脚本执行方式，不使用 cmd\n\n## Critical Context\n- 项目路径: `C:\\Use