{"type":"message","id":"340dc0bc","parentId":"16ad3007","timestamp":"2026-06-12T09:18:37.998Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"没有图像参数缓存。在 `ptz_config.json` 中添加 `image_params` 字段，在读取和设置时更新缓存。\n\n**步骤：**\n1. 连接成功后，读取并缓存图像参数到 ptz_config.json\n2. 前端刷新时，优先从缓存读取\n3. 设置参数时，更新缓存\n\n这需要较大改动。根据\"禁止过度开发\"原则，采用更简单的方式：**在 `get_connected_device` API 返回时同时返回缓存的图像参数**。\n\n先更新版本号到 v6.02："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_530657566fb943b89ba9a14e","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"<span class=\"version\">v6.02</span>","oldText":"<span class=\"version\">v6.01</span>"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":144129,"output":196,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":144325,"cost":{"input":0.144129,"output":0.0006272000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1447562}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781255869167,"responseId":"cht000d10c4@dx19ebb1f9a15b9cb212"}}
