{"type":"message","id":"d2545217","parentId":"a148abf6","timestamp":"2026-06-12T09:43:19.239Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到 `/ptz/{device_id}/function` API。它读取的是 `data/{device_model}/*/function.json`，不是 `src/advanced/device_config.json`。\n\n检查 `get_device_function` 实现："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_076b0bcf1bb7479796ac3a90","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":2525,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":157413,"output":91,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":157504,"cost":{"input":0.157413,"output":0.00029120000000000003,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1577042}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781257386256,"responseId":"cht000d66e7@dx19ebb36cbb4b828232"}}
{"type":"message","id":"abf154e7","parentId":"d2545217","timestamp":"2026-06-12T09:43:19.246Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_076b0bcf1bb7479796ac3a90","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"@api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/function\", summary=\"获取设备function.json\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def get_device_function(device_id: str) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"从 data/{device_model}/*/function.json 读取设备功能参数范围。\"\"\"\r\n    import json\r\n    from pathlib import Path\r\n    mgr: PTZManager | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_manager\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZManager 未初始化\"}\r\n    \r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n    \r\n    # 从 data 目录查找 function.json\r\n    data_dir = Path(__file__).resolve().parent.parent.parent / \"data\"\r\n    if not data_dir.exists():\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"data 目录不存在\", \"data\": None}\r\n    \r\n    # 遍历所有子目录查找 function.json\r\n    for subdir in data_dir.iterdir():\r\n        if subdir.is_dir():\r\n            for f in subdir.rglob(\"function.json\"):\r\n                try:\r\n                    with open(f, \"r\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as fh:\r\n                        func_data = json.load(fh)\r\n                    # 检查 IP 是否匹配\r\n                    if func_data.get(\"device_info\", {}).get(\"ip\") == target_ip:\r\n                        return {\"success\": True, \"data\": func_data}\r\n                except Exception:\r\n                    continue\r\n    \r\n    return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"未找到该设备的 function.json\", \"data\": None}\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/whitebalance\", summary=\"获取白平衡设置\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def get_whitebalance(device_id: str) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"获取设备白平衡当前设置。\"\"\"\r\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n    mgr: PTZManager | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_manager\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZManager 未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n\r\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n\n[552 more lines in file. Use offset=2575 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781257399246}}
{"type":"message","id":"13029f9a","parentId":"abf154e7","timestamp":"2026-06-12T09:43:47.823Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"`get_device_function` 返回的是 `data/{device_model}/*/function.json`，这是 function 运行后的结果。\n\n而 `src/advanced/device_config.json` 是全局配置，包含所有设备的参数。\n\n**结论：**\n- `device_config.json` 已有 `current_values` 字段\n- 前端应该读取这个文件，而不是从设备重新读取\n\n修改方案：让 `/api/v1/ptz/{ip}/function` 返回 `device_config.json` 的数据。\n\n但这样会改变原有逻辑。更好的方案：**添加新 API `/api/v1/ptz/image-params-cached`**，从 `device_config.json` 返回缓存值。\n\n老板，图像参数已经在 `src/advanced/device_config.json` 的 `current_values` 字段中存储了。问题在于前端刷新时没有读取这个缓存。\n\n**修复方案：**\n前端 `loadDeviceImageParams` 先调用 `/api/v1/advanced/function/status` 获取 `device_config.json` 的数据，如果缓存存在则用缓存值初始化 UI，然后再从设备读取最新值更新缓存。\n\n这样：\n1. 刷新页面时 UI 立即显示缓存值\n2. 后台从设备读取最新值更新\n3. 无需重新连接设备\n\n是否继续实现？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":146681,"output":273,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":146954,"cost":{"input":0.146681,"output":0.0008736000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1475546}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781257399252,"responseId":"cht000d1a15@dx19ebb36ff96b85e102"}}
{"type":"message","id":"cc9a1b4f","parentId":"13029f9a","timestamp":"2026-06-12T09:44:36.469Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"33559\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-06-12 17:44 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n不对，src/advanced/device_config.json这个里面保存的是什么信息？我的function脚本储存的位置和文件是什么？这两个文件有什么区别？"}],"timestamp":1781257476462}}
