{"type":"message","id":"f6a3c980","parentId":"7cfe6c99","timestamp":"2026-06-12T10:11:06.389Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_49d87aab07de4d3299937e87","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\doc\\data_storage.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":63818,"output":31,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63849,"cost":{"input":0.063818,"output":0.00009920000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0639172}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781259062599,"responseId":"cht000e2d26@dx19ebb504eedb893102"}}
{"type":"message","id":"70e8ba95","parentId":"f6a3c980","timestamp":"2026-06-12T10:11:06.396Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_49d87aab07de4d3299937e87","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 数据存储设计文档\n\n> 版本: v1.0\n> 更新: 2026-05-23\n> 作者: 开发工厂\n\n## 1. 设计目标\n\n- 多设备支持：每设备独立数据目录\n- 数据隔离：功能探测/限位/速度分开存储\n- 非硬编码路径：基于项目根目录动态计算\n- 增量更新：只更新变化部分\n\n## 2. 目录结构\n\n```\nastrohub/\n├── data/\n│   ├── config.json              # 全局配置\n│   ├── registry.json            # 设备注册表\n│   └── devices/\n│       └── {device_id}/         # 设备目录（按MAC生成ID）\n│           ├── info.json        # 设备基础信息\n│           ├── status.json      # 实时状态\n│           ├── function.json    # 功能探测结果\n│           ├── limit.json       # 限位测试结果\n│           ├── speed.json       # 速度测试结果\n│           ├── calibration.json # 校准数据\n│           └── presets.json     # 预置点列表\n```\n\n## 3. 数据结构定义\n\n### 3.1 config.json - 全局配置\n\n```json\n{\n  \"version\": \"5.29\",\n  \"server\": {\n    \"port\": 10280,\n    \"host\": \"0.0.0.0\"\n  },\n  \"network\": {\n    \"selected_interface\": \"以太网\",\n    \"local_ip\": \"192.168.5.64\"\n  },\n  \"defaults\": {\n    \"username\": \"admin\",\n    \"password\": \"\",\n    \"port\": 80\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 3.2 registry.json - 设备注册表\n\n```json\n{\n  \"devices\": {\n    \"{mac}\": {\n      \"id\": \"dev_001\",\n      \"name\": \"摄像头1\",\n      \"model\": \"iDS-2DF8C832IXS-A\",\n      \"ip\": \"192.168.5.72\",\n      \"last_seen\": \"2026-05-23T13:44:00\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"active_device\": \"dev_001\"\n}\n```\n\n### 3.3 devices/{device_id}/info.json\n\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"dev_001\",\n  \"mac\": \"24-0f-9b-76-41-93\",\n  \"ip\": \"192.168.5.72\",\n  \"port\": 80,\n  \"model\": \"iDS-2DF8C832IXS-A\",\n  \"serial\": \"\",\n  \"firmware\": \"\",\n  \"credentials\": {\n    \"username\": \"admin\",\n    \"password\": \"\"\n  },\n  \"channels\": 1,\n  \"created\": \"2026-05-23T10:00:00\",\n  \"updated\": \"2026-05-23T13:44:00\"\n}\n```\n\n### 3.4 devices/{device_id}/function.json\n\n```json\n{\n  \"device_id\": \"dev_001\",\n  \"detected_at\": \"2026-05-23T13:38:00\",\n  \"summary\": {\n    \"total\": 20,\n    \"supported\": 20,\n    \"modifiable\": 6\n  },\n  \"results\": {\n    \"P4.1\": {\n      \"label\": \"IrLED 红外补光\",\n      \"supported\": true,\n      \"modifiable\": false,\n      \"range\": {\"min\": 1, \"max\": 100},\n      \"current\": {\"brightnessLimit\": 50},\n      \"endpoint\": \"/Image/channels/1/IrLight\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 3.5 devices/{device_id}/limit.json\n\n```json\n{\n  \"device_id\": \"dev_001\",\n  \"tested_at\": \"2026-05-23T14:00:00\",\n  \"results\": {\n    \"P6.0\": {\n      \"label\": \"左限位\",\n      \"supported\": true,\n      \"limit_angle\": 180.5,\n      \"current_angle\": 0.0,\n      \"reached\": true\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 3.6 devices/{device_id}/speed.json\n\n```json\n{\n  \"device_id\": \"dev_001\",\n  \"tested_at\": \"2026-05-23T14:30:00\",\n  \"results\": {\n    \"pan\": {\n      \"speed_100\": {\"time_ms\": 3200, \"degrees\": 360},\n      \"speed_50\": {\"time_ms\": 6400, \"degrees\": 360}\n    },\n    \"tilt\": {\n      \"speed_100\": {\"time_ms\": 2800, \"degrees\": 90}\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## 4. API 接口\n\n### 4.1 DataStore 类\n\n```python\nfrom src.storage.store import DataStore\n\n# 初始化（自动定位项目根目录）\nstore = DataStore()\n\n# 设备管理\nstore.register_device(mac, ip, model, credentials)\nstore.get_device(mac) -> dict\nstore.list_devices() -> list[dict]\nstore.set_active_device(mac)\n\n# 功能探测\nstore.save_function_results(device_id, results)\nstore.get_function_results(device_id) -> dict\n\n# 限位测试\nstore.save_limit_results(device_id, results)\nstore.get_limit_results(device_id) -> dict\n\n# 速度测试\nstore.save_speed_results(device_id, results)\nstore.get_speed_results(device_id) -> dict\n\n# 全局配置\nstore.get_config() -> dict\nstore.update_config(key, value)\n```\n\n## 5. 设备ID生成规则\n\n- 格式：`dev_{序号}`，如 `dev_001`, `dev_002`\n- 序号从注册表自动递增\n- MAC地址作为唯一标识，设备ID仅用于目录命名\n\n## 6. 数据更新策略\n\n| 场景 | 操作 |\n|------|------|\n| 新设备连接 | 注册设备，创建目录，写入 info.json |\n| 功能探测完成 | 更新 function.json |\n| 限位测试完成 | 更新 limit.json |\n| 设备状态变化 | 更新 status.json |\n| 配置修改 | 更新 config.json |\n\n## 7. 错误处理\n\n- 目录不存在：自动创建\n- 文件不存在：返回默认值\n- JSON解析失败：返回默认值并记录日志\n- 写入失败：抛出异常\n\n## 8. 迁移计划\n\n现有 `device_config.json` 迁移到新结构：\n\n1. 读取现有 `device_config.json`\n2. 按 MAC 注册设备\n3. 分离 function_detection 到 function.json\n4. 删除旧文件\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781259066396}}
