{"type":"message","id":"665e3bc4","parentId":"e0e0c501","timestamp":"2026-06-12T10:23:28.080Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ad822a5521884f73929ecfc1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\nsrc/core/ptz_flow.py - M1 PTZ 发现与配置完整流程编排 (P1-P3)\n\n实现步骤:\n  P1  : 收集本机硬件/网络信息, 物理网卡选择\n  P1.1: 收集主机硬件 (hostname/CPU/RAM/GPU/VRAM)\n  P1.2: 枚举物理网卡 (排除虚拟/隧道)\n  P1.3: 用户选择网卡 (单网卡自动, 多网卡交互)\n  P2  : SADP 发现 + IP 修改\n  P2.1: SADP 扫描发现设备 (10秒窗口)\n  P2.2: 设备型号识别 + MAC 匹配\n  P2.3: 激活状态检测\n  P2.4: IP 可达性判断 (PING)\n  P2.5: 修改设备 IP (同网段 .64, 占用时找下一个)\n  P2.6: 保存设备凭证到 PTZ_config.json\n  P3  : ISAPI 认证\n  P3.1: 用户输入账号密码\n  P3.2: GET /ISAPI/System/deviceInfo 验证\n\nAuthor: 雅痞张@南方天文\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport json\nimport os\nimport platform\nimport subprocess\nimport time\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Optional\n\nimport xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n\nfrom src.config_paths import CONFIG_DIR, ensure_directories\nfrom src.core.nic_selector import (\n    NICInfo,\n    get_physical_nic_display,\n    get_selected_nic_info,\n    list_physical_nics,\n    select_nic,\n)\nfrom src.core.net_detector import find_available_ip, suggest_target_ip\nfrom src.core.ptz_manager import check_reachable\nfrom src.core.sadp_discovery import (\n    SADPManager,\n    SADPDevice,\n    sadp_error_message,\n)\n\n\n[870 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781259808080}}
{"type":"message","id":"bd395955","parentId":"665e3bc4","timestamp":"2026-06-12T10:23:52.396Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"更新文件头部文档和 import："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6923c7aeedda4f92b4211285","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"\"\"\"\nsrc/core/startup.py - M1 启动检测流程 (P1-P3)\n\n实现步骤:\n  P1  : 收集本机硬件/网络信息, 物理网卡选择\n  P1.1: 收集主机硬件 (hostname/CPU/RAM/GPU/VRAM)\n  P1.2: 枚举物理网卡 (排除虚拟/隧道)\n  P1.3: 用户选择网卡 (单网卡自动, 多网卡交互)\n  P2  : SADP 发现 + IP 修改\n  P2.1: SADP 扫描发现设备 (10秒窗口)\n  P2.2: 设备型号识别 + MAC 匹配\n  P2.3: 激活状态检测\n  P2.4: IP 可达性判断 (PING)\n  P2.5: 修改设备 IP (同网段 .64, 占用时找下一个)\n  P2.6: 保存设备信息到 data/devices/{mac}/info.json + registry.json\n  P3  : ISAPI 认证\n  P3.1: 用户输入账号密码\n  P3.2: GET /ISAPI/System/deviceInfo 验证\n\n输出文件:\n  - data/system.json: 本机系统信息\n  - data/registry.json: 设备注册表\n  - data/devices/{mac}/info.json: 设备详情\n\nAuthor: 雅痞张@南方天文\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport json\nimport os\nimport platform\nimport subprocess\nimport time\nfrom datetime import datetime, timezone\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Optional\n\nimport xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n\nfrom src.config_paths import CONFIG_DIR, DATA_DIR, ensure_directories, DEVICES_DIR, REGISTRY_FILE, SYSTEM_FILE","oldText":"\"\"\"\nsrc/core/ptz_flow.py - M1 PTZ 发现与配置完整流程编排 (P1-P3)\n\n实现步骤:\n  P1  : 收集本机硬件/网络信息, 物理网卡选择\n  P1.1: 收集主机硬件 (hostname/CPU/RAM/GPU/VRAM)\n  P1.2: 枚举物理网卡 (排除虚拟/隧道)\n  P1.3: 用户选择网卡 (单网卡自动, 多网卡交互)\n  P2  : SADP 发现 + IP 修改\n  P2.1: SADP 扫描发现设备 (10秒窗口)\n  P2.2: 设备型号识别 + MAC 匹配\n  P2.3: 激活状态检测\n  P2.4: IP 可达性判断 (PING)\n  P2.5: 修改设备 IP (同网段 .64, 占用时找下一个)\n  P2.6: 保存设备凭证到 PTZ_config.json\n  P3  : ISAPI 认证\n  P3.1: 用户输入账号密码\n  P3.2: GET /ISAPI/System/deviceInfo 验证\n\nAuthor: 雅痞张@南方天文\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport json\nimport os\nimport platform\nimport subprocess\nimport time\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Optional\n\nimport xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n\nfrom src.config_paths im