{"type":"message","id":"fa221c0a","parentId":"df239912","timestamp":"2026-06-12T10:30:48.166Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**步骤 8：更新文档**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a8c498824a754eae8cd0169a","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 数据存储设计文档\n\n> 版本: v6.03\n> 更新: 2026-06-12\n> 作者: 开发工厂\n\n## 1. 设计目标\n\n- **Portable 应用**：整个程序可移植，所有数据相对于程序目录\n- **多设备支持**：每设备独立数据目录\n- **数据隔离**：功能探测/限位/速度分开存储\n- **动态路径**：禁止硬编码，基于项目根目录动态计算\n- **时间戳记录**：每次测试生成带时间戳文件，读取时选最新\n\n## 2. 目录结构\n\n```\nastrohub/\n├── data/\n│   ├── system.json              # 本机系统信息\n│   ├── registry.json            # 设备注册表\n│   └── devices/\n│       └── {mac}/               # 设备目录（MAC地址，无冒号小写）\n│           ├── info.json        # 设备基础信息 + 凭据\n│           ├── function_20260612_181530.json    # 功能探测结果（带时间戳）\n│           ├── limit_20260612_182000.json       # 限位测试结果\n│           ├── speed_20260612_182500.json       # 速度测试结果\n│           └── calibration.json                 # 校准数据\n```\n\n## 3. 数据结构定义\n\n### 3.1 system.json - 本机系统信息\n\n```json\n{\n  \"hostname\": \"Astro-AIO\",\n  \"cpu_model\": \"Intel i7-12700K\",\n  \"ram_gb\": 32,\n  \"selected_nic\": {\n    \"name\": \"以太网\",\n    \"ip\": \"192.168.5.64\",\n    \"mac\": \"00-11-22-33-44-55\"\n  },\n  \"last_check\": \"2026-06-12T18:20:00\"\n}\n```\n\n### 3.2 registry.json - 设备注册表\n\n```json\n{\n  \"devices\": {\n    \"240f9b764193\": {\n      \"name\": \"4k 32X DC\",\n      \"model\": \"iDS-2DF8C832IXS-A\",\n      \"ip\": \"192.168.5.72\",\n      \"last_seen\": \"2026-06-12T18:20:00\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"active_device\": \"240f9b764193\"\n}\n```\n\n### 3.3 devices/{mac}/info.json - 设备详情\n\n```json\n{\n  \"mac\": \"24-0F-9B-76-41-93\",\n  \"ip\": \"192.168.5.72\",\n  \"port\": 80,\n  \"model\": \"iDS-2DF8C832IXS-A\",\n  \"serial_number\": \"iDS-2DF8C832IXS-A20211211CCCHJ22538548\",\n  \"firmware_version\": \"V5.8.0\",\n  \"name\": \"4k 32X DC\",\n  \"credentials\": {\n    \"username\": \"admin\",\n    \"password\": \"Nftw1357\"\n  },\n  \"network\": {\n    \"gateway\": \"192.168.5.1\",\n    \"subnet_mask\": \"255.255.255.0\"\n  },\n  \"first_seen\": \"2026-05-29T10:00:00\",\n  \"last_updated\": \"2026-06-12T18:20:00\",\n  \"onboarding_complete\": true\n}\n```\n\n### 3.4 devices/{mac}/function_{timestamp}.json - 功能探测结果\n\n```json\n{\n  \"device_info\": {\n    \"ip\": \"192.168.5.72\",\n    \"mac\": \"240f9b764193\",\n    \"model\": \"iDS-2DF8C\"\n  },\n  \"detected_at\": \"2026-06-12T18:15:30\",\n  \"function_detection\": {\n    \"P4.1\": {\n      \"p_id\": \"P4.1\",\n      \"item\": \"ir_led\",\n      \"label\": \"IrLED 红外补光\",\n      \"supported\": true,\n      \"endpoint\": \"/Image/channels/1/IrLight\",\n      \"min_val\": 1,\n      \"max_val\": 100,\n      \"current_values\": {\"brightnessLimit\": 50},\n      \"test_results\": [{\"value\": 50, \"success\": true}],\n      \"restored\": true,\n      \"error\": null\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 3.5 devices/{mac}/limit_{timestamp}.json - 限位测试结果\n\n```json\n{\n  \"device_id\": \"240f9b764193\",\n  \"tested_at\": \"2026-06-12T18:20:00\",\n  \"results\": {\n    \"pan_min\": 0.0,\n    \"pan_max\": 360.0,\n    \"tilt_min\": -90.0,\n    \"tilt_max\": 45.0\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 3.6 devices/{mac}/speed_{timestamp}.json - 速度测试结果\n\n```json\n{\n  \"device_id\": \"240f9b764193\",\n  \"tested_at\": \"2026-06-12T18:25:00\",\n  \"results\": {\n    \"pan\": {\n      \"speed_100\": {\"time_ms\": 3200, \"degrees\": 360},\n      \"speed_50\": {\"time_ms\": 6400, \"degrees\": 360}\n    },\n    \"tilt\": {\n      \"speed_100\": {\"time_ms\": 2800, \"degrees\": 90}\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## 4. 核心模块\n\n### 4.1 config_paths.py - 路径常量\n\n```python\nfrom src.config_paths import (\n    DATA_DIR,        # data/\n    DEVICES_DIR,     # data/devices/\n    SYSTEM_FILE,     # data/system.json\n    REGISTRY_FILE,   # data/registry.json\n)\n```\n\n### 4.2 device_path.py - 动态路径\n\n```python\nfrom src.advanced.device_path import (\n    get_device_info,      # 获取设备标识信息\n    get_device_dir,       # 获取设备目录\n    get_data_path_read,   # 获取读取路径（最新文件）\n    get_data_path_write,  # 获取写入路径（带时间戳）\n)\n```\n\n### 4.3 startup.py - 启动检测\n\n```python\nfrom src.core.startup import M1Flow\n\nflow = M1Flow()\nresult = flow.run_full_flow()  # P1-P3 完整流程\n```\n\n## 5. 数据更新策略\n\n| 场景 | 操作 |\n|------|------|\n| 启动时 | 检查 system.json、registry.json 完整性 |\n| 新设备发现 | 创建 devices/{mac}/info.json |\n| 功能探测完成 | 写入 function_{timestamp}.json |\n| 限位测试完成 | 写入 limit_{timestamp}.json |\n| 速度测试完成 | 写入 speed_{timestamp}.json |\n| 读取数据时 | 选择最新时间戳文件 |\n\n## 6. 迁移说明\n\nv6.03 之前的数据文件：\n\n| 旧文件 | 新位置 |\n|--------|--------|\n| `data/config/ptz_config.json` | `data/devices/{mac}/info.json` |\n| `data/device_config.json` | `data/registry.json` |\n| `data/{model}_{mac}/{date}_*/function.json` | `data/devices/{mac}/function_{timestamp}.json` |\n| `src/advanced/device_config.json` | 删除（不再使用） |\n\n## 7. 错误处理\n\n- 目录不存在：自动创建\n- 文件不存在：返回默认值\n- JSON解析失败：返回默认值并记录日志\n- 写入失败：抛出异常\n","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\doc\\data_storage.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":100020,"output":1776,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101796,"cost":{"input":0.10002,"output":0.0056832,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1057032}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781260210457,"responseId":"cht000df6b3@dx19ebb61d369b9ca102"}}
