{"type":"message","id":"61b76a42","parentId":"9dd7a8fb","timestamp":"2026-06-12T17:27:33.220Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e00c201d8ff94ef0836a1cd3","name":"memory_get","arguments":{"lines":100,"path":"memory/2026-06-12.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":47084,"output":25,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47109,"cost":{"input":0.047084,"output":0.00008,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.047164}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781285247281,"responseId":"cht000d0979@dx19ebcdfe4dbba5a412"}}
{"type":"message","id":"4ed89488","parentId":"61b76a42","timestamp":"2026-06-12T17:27:33.228Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e00c201d8ff94ef0836a1cd3","toolName":"memory_get","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"text\": \"# 2026-06-12 Memory\\n\\n## v6.10 数据存储路径重构\\n\\n### 核心修改\\n1. **路径统一**: 所有设备数据迁移到 `data/devices/{mac}/` 目录\\n2. **MAC 格式**: 统一为无分隔符小写（如 `240f9b764193`）\\n3. **删除旧文件**: `ptz_config.json`、`device_config.json`\\n\\n### 修改文件\\n- `src/config_paths.py` - 添加 DEVICES_DIR、REGISTRY_FILE\\n- `src/core/ptz_manager.py` - ConfigManager 使用新路径\\n- `src/core/device_manager.py` - DeviceManager 使用新路径\\n- `src/core/startup.py` - 保存设备到 devices/{mac}/info.json\\n- `src/advanced/device_path.py` - 统一路径函数\\n- `src/advanced/function.py` - 输出到动态路径\\n- `src/main/main.py` - 修复 get_module 问题\\n- `src/api/router.py` - `_resolve_device_id_to_ip` 支持无分隔符 MAC\\n\\n### 关键教训\\n1. **_normalize_mac 统一**: 必须全局一致，无分隔符小写避免目录名不匹配\\n2. **Orchestrator 不是模块管理器**: main.py 直接创建 PTZManager 实例\\n3. **热重载问题**: 使用 --reload 时 _managers 可能未正确初始化\\n4. **router.py MAC 格式**: `_resolve_device_id_to_ip` 需同时支持冒号、横杠、无分隔符格式\\n\\n### 数据结构\\n```\\ndata/\\n├── devices/\\n│   └── {mac}/\\n│       ├── info.json              # 设备信息\\n│       ├── function_{ts}.json     # 功能探测\\n│       ├── limit_{ts}.json        # 限位测试\\n│       └── speed_{ts}.json        # 速度测试\\n└── registry.json                  # 设备注册表\\n```\\n\\n## v6.11 Playwright E2E 测试\\n\\n### 测试结果\\n- 主页加载 ✅\\n- 版本号显示 v6.11 ✅\\n- 设备列表渲染 ✅\\n- 设备在线状态 ✅\\n- 断开按钮显示 ✅\\n\\n### 测试文件\\n- `tests/e2e_test.py` - Playwright 自动化测试\\n\\n### E2E 测试要点\\n1. **等待渲染**: 切换页面后需 `wait_for_timeout(3000)` 等待 JS 加载\\n2. **tbody 结构**: `#deviceTable` 是 `<tbody>`，行数=数据行数\\n3. **按钮状态**: 设备在线显示\\\"断开\\\"按钮，离线显示\\\"连接\\\"按钮\\n\",\n  \"path\": \"memory/2026-06-12.md\",\n  \"from\": 1,\n  \"lines\": 54\n}"}],"details":{"text":"# 2026-06-12 Memory\n\n## v6.10 数据存储路径重构\n\n### 核心修改\n1. **路径统一**: 所有设备数据迁移到 `data/devices/{mac}/` 目录\n2. **MAC 格式**: 统一为无分隔符小写（如 `240f9b764193`）\n3. **删除旧文件**: `ptz_config.json`、`device_config.json`\n\n### 修改文件\n- `src/config_paths.py` - 添加 DEVICES_DIR、REGISTRY_FILE\n- `src/core/ptz_manager.py` - ConfigManager 使用新路径\n- `src/core/device_manager.py` - DeviceManager 使用新路径\n- `src/core/startup.py` - 保存设备到 devices/{mac}/info.json\n- `src/advanced/device_path.py` - 统一路径函数\n- `src/advanced/function.py` - 输出到动态路径\n- `src/main/main.py` - 修复 get_module 问题\n- `src/api/router.py` - `_resolve_device_id_to_ip` 支持无分隔符 MAC\n\n### 关键教训\n1. **_normalize_mac 统一**: 必须全局一致，无分隔符小写避免目录名不匹配\n2. **Orchestrator 不是模块管理器**: main.py 直接创建 PTZManager 实例\n3. **热重载问题**: 使用 --reload 时 _managers 可能未正确初始化\n4. **router.py MAC 格式**: `_resolve_device_id_to_ip` 需同时支持冒号、横杠、无分隔符格式\n\n### 数据结构\n```\ndata/\n├── devices/\n│   └── {mac}/\n│       ├── info.json              # 设备信息\n│       ├── function_{ts}.json     # 功能探测\n│       ├── limit_{ts}.json        # 限位测试\n│       └── speed_{ts}.json        # 速度测试\n└── registry.json                  # 设备注册表\n```\n\n## v6.11 Playwright E2E 测试\n\n### 测试结果\n- 主页加载 ✅\n- 版本号显示 v6.11 ✅\n- 设备列表渲染 ✅\n- 设备在线状态 ✅\n- 断开按钮显示 ✅\n\n### 测试文件\n- `tests/e2e_test.py` - Playwright 自动化测试\n\n### E2E 测试要点\n1. **等待渲染**: 切换页面后需 `wait_for_timeout(3000)` 等待 JS 加载\n2. **tbody 结构**: `#deviceTable` 是 `<tbody>`，行数=数据行数\n3. **按钮状态**: 设备在线显示\"断开\"按钮，离线显示\"连接\"按钮\n","path":"memory/2026-06-12.md","from":1,"lines":54},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781285253228}}
{"type":"message","id":"437bc399","parentId":"4ed89488","timestamp":"2026-06-12T17:27:40.822Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"没有记录。我来检查代码，找出**真正的问题根源**："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-f4e07e6cc4a948e294f697bd2a3e06eb","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":80,"offset":382,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":45438,"output":60,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45498,"cost":{"input":0.045438,"output":0.000192,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.04563}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781285253229,"responseId":"cht000d6290@dx19ebcdffa4bba60352"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3e5c5999","parentId":"437bc399","timestamp":"2026-06-12T17:27:40.829Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-f4e07e6cc4a948e294f697bd2a3e06eb","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"function loadDeviceImageParams(deviceIp) {\n    if (!deviceIp) return;\n    \n    // 检查 apiGet 是否可用\n    if (typeof apiGet === 'undefined') {\n        console.error('[IMAGE] apiGet not defined, cannot load image params');\n        return;\n    }\n    \n    console.log('[IMAGE] Loading image params for:', deviceIp);\n    \n    // v5.42: 先加载 function.json 获取参数范围\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/function').then(function(r) {\n        if (r && r.success && r.data) {\n            deviceFunctionData = r.data;\n            console.log('[IMAGE] function.json loaded:', r.data.functions);\n        }\n    }).catch(function(e) {\n        console.warn('[IMAGE] function.json load failed:', e);\n    });\n    \n    // 加载曝光模式\n    loadExposure(deviceIp);\n    \n    // 加载 OSD 状态\n    loadOsdStatus(deviceIp);\n    \n    // 加载白平衡\n    loadWhiteBalance(deviceIp);\n    \n    // 加载降噪\n    loadNoiseReduce(deviceIp);\n    \n    // 加载快门\n    loadShutter(deviceIp);\n    \n    // 加载光圈\n    loadIris(deviceIp);\n    \n    // 加载锐度\n    loadSharpness(deviceIp);\n    \n    // 加载亮度/对比度/饱和度\n    loadColorParams(deviceIp);\n}\n\n// 加载 OSD 状态\nfunction loadOsdStatus(deviceIp) {\n    // PTZ OSD\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/osd/ptz').then(function(r) {\n        if (r && r.success) {\n            var enabled = r.enabled || r.data?.enabled || false;\n            updatePtzOsdButtons(enabled);\n            // 保存到 localStorage\n            localStorage.setItem('osd_ptz_' + deviceIp, enabled ? '1' : '0');\n        } else {\n            // 从 localStorage 读取上次设置\n            var saved = localStorage.getItem('osd_ptz_' + deviceIp);\n            if (saved !== null) {\n                updatePtzOsdButtons(saved === '1');\n            }\n        }\n    }).catch(function(e) {\n        var saved = localStorage.getItem('osd_ptz_' + deviceIp);\n        if (saved !== null) {\n            updatePtzOsdButtons(saved === '1');\n        }\n    });\n    \n    // Info OSD\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/osd/info').then(function(r) {\n        if (r && r.success) {\n            var enabled = r.enabled || r.data?.enabled || false;\n            updateInfoOsdButtons(enabled);\n            localStorage.setItem('osd_info_' + deviceIp, enabled ? '1' : '0');\n        } else {\n            var saved = localStorage.getItem('osd_info_' + deviceIp);\n            if (saved !== null) {\n                updateInfoOsdButtons(saved === '1');\n            }\n\n[540 more lines in file. Use offset=462 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781285260829}}
{"type":"message","id":"c283b1d4","parentId":"3e5c5999","timestamp":"2026-06-12T17:28:04.875Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**问题根源发现：**\n\n`loadDeviceImageParams` 是异步调用，但 **`apiGet('/function')` 没有等待完成** 就调用了 `loadShutter/loadIris`，导致 `deviceFunctionData` 还没加载完成！\n\n**之前我做了什么：**\n- 添加了 `loadDeviceImageParams` 调用 ✅\n- 但**没有修复异步顺序问题** ❌\n\n**正确修复：**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4abd35cf74b44f49839e69d2","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"function loadDeviceImageParams(deviceIp) {\n    if (!deviceIp) return;\n    \n    // 检查 apiGet 是否可用\n    if (typeof apiGet === 'undefined') {\n        console.error('[IMAGE] apiGet not defined, cannot load image params');\n        return;\n    }\n    \n    console.log('[IMAGE] Loading image params for:', deviceIp);\n    \n    // v6.12: 先加载 function.json 获取参数范围，等待完成后再加载其他参数\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/function').then(function(r) {\n        if (r && r.success && r.data) {\n            deviceFunctionData = r.data;\n            console.log('[IMAGE] function.json loaded:', r.data.functions);\n        }\n        \n        // v6.12: function 加载完成后再加载其他参数（需要 deviceFunctionData）\n        loadExposure(deviceIp);\n        loadOsdStatus(deviceIp);\n        loadWhiteBalance(deviceIp);\n        loadNoiseReduce(deviceIp);\n        loadShutter(deviceIp);\n        loadIris(deviceIp);\n        loadSharpness(deviceIp);\n        loadColorParams(deviceIp);\n    }).catch(function(e) {\n        console.warn('[IMAGE] function.json load failed:', e);\n        // 即使失败也尝试加载其他参数\n        loadExposure(deviceIp);\n        loadOsdStatus(deviceIp);\n        loadWhiteBalance(deviceIp);\n        loadNoiseReduce(deviceIp);\n        loadShutter(deviceIp);\n        loadIris(deviceIp);\n        loadSharpness(deviceIp);\n        loadColorParams(deviceIp);\n    });\n}","oldText":"function loadDeviceImageParams(deviceIp) {\n    if (!deviceIp) return;\n    \n    // 检查 apiGet 是否可用\n    if (typeof apiGet === 'undefined') {\n        console.error('[IMAGE] apiGet not defined, cannot load image params');\n        return;\n    }\n    \n    console.log('[IMAGE] Loading image params for:', deviceIp);\n    \n    // v5.42: 先加载 function.json 获取参数范围\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/function').then(function(r) {\n        if (r && r.success && r.data) {\n            deviceFunctionData = r.data;\n            console.log('[IMAGE] function.json loaded:', r.data.functions);\n        }\n    }).catch(function(e) {\n        console.warn('[IMAGE] function.json load failed:', e);\n    });\n    \n    // 加载曝光模式\n    loadExposure(deviceIp);\n    \n    // 加载 OSD 状态\n    loadOsdStatus(deviceIp);\n    \n    // 加载白平衡\n    loadWhiteBalance(deviceIp);\n    \n    // 加载降噪\n    loadNoiseReduce(deviceIp);\n    \n    // 加载快门\n    loadShutter(deviceIp);\n    \n    // 加载光圈\n    loadIris(deviceIp);\n    \n    // 加载锐度\n    loadSharpness(deviceIp);\n    \n    // 加载亮度/对比度/饱和度\n    loadColorParams(deviceIp);\n}"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":48646,"output":868,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49514,"cost":{"input":0.048645999999999995,"output":0.0027776000000000003,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.05142359999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781285260830,"responseId":"cht000d1c1e@dx19ebce01abdb8ab282"}}
