{"type":"message","id":"25e33a6b","parentId":"4bed52a7","timestamp":"2026-06-12T17:29:11.501Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c5ecfbe5e3a94d9fa13b2a87","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[TEST] ����ҳ...\r\n[PASS] ��ҳ���سɹ�\r\n[INFO] �汾: v6.13\r\n[TEST] �л����豸����...\r\n[INFO] �豸����: 1\r\n[DEBUG] ��������: <tr><td><span class=\"badge manual\">�ֶ�</span></td><td>240f9b764193</td><td>192.168.5.72</td><td>--</td><td>4k 32X DC</td><td>iDS-2DF8C832IXS-A</td><td><span class=\"badge online\">����</span></td><td><div ...\r\n[PASS] �豸�б���ʾ����\r\n[TEST] ����豸������ť...\r\n[PASS] �豸�����ߣ���ʾ�Ͽ���ť\r\n[INFO] ��ͼ�ѱ���\r\n\r\n[PASS] ���в���ͨ��\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"vivid-bloom","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[TEST] ����ҳ...\r\n[PASS] ��ҳ���سɹ�\r\n[INFO] �汾: v6.13\r\n[TEST] �л����豸����...\r\n[INFO] �豸����: 1\r\n[DEBUG] ��������: <tr><td><span class=\"badge manual\">�ֶ�</span></td><td>240f9b764193</td><td>192.168.5.72</td><td>--</td><td>4k 32X DC</td><td>iDS-2DF8C832IXS-A</td><td><span class=\"badge online\">����</span></td><td><div ...\r\n[PASS] �豸�б���ʾ����\r\n[TEST] ����豸������ť...\r\n[PASS] �豸�����ߣ���ʾ�Ͽ���ť\r\n[INFO] ��ͼ�ѱ���\r\n\r\n[PASS] ���в���ͨ��\r\n","name":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.opencl...s\\dev-factory\\astrohub"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781285351501}}
{"type":"message","id":"9ea13324","parentId":"25e33a6b","timestamp":"2026-06-12T17:29:25.749Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**E2E 测试通过。记录问题根源到记忆文件：**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-54bd3850499b460cb337f216f1430753","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 2026-06-13 记忆\n\n## v6.13 异步加载修复\n\n### 问题根源\n老板反馈：白平衡、快门、光圈刷新后不加载，已修复4次仍然无效。\n\n**真正原因**：`loadDeviceImageParams` 中 `apiGet('/function')` 和后续 `loadShutter/loadIris` 是**并行执行**，不是顺序执行！\n\n```javascript\n// 错误写法（之前）：\napiGet('/function').then(...);  // 异步，不等待\nloadShutter(deviceIp);          // 立即执行，deviceFunctionData 还未加载\n\n// 正确写法（现在）：\napiGet('/function').then(function(r) {\n    deviceFunctionData = r.data;  // 先加载完成\n    loadShutter(deviceIp);        // 再调用依赖函数\n});\n```\n\n### 关键教训\n1. **JavaScript Promise 不阻塞**：`.then()` 后的代码立即执行，不会等待\n2. **依赖数据必须嵌套在 .then() 内**：需要 `deviceFunctionData` 的函数必须在 Promise 成功回调内调用\n3. **相同问题反复出现 = 根本原因未找到**：不要只看表面调用，要看执行顺序\n\n### 其他修复\n- OSD 开关状态同步：`updatePtzOsdButtons/updateInfoOsdButtons` 添加开关状态更新\n- 降噪提示：`setNoiseReduce` 添加 `showToast` 反馈\n- WASM 状态：`clickStartRealPlay` 成功后调用 `updateWasmStatus('connected')`","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\memory\\2026-06-13.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":49900,"output":398,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50298,"cost":{"input":0.0499,"output":0.0012736000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0511736}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781285351503,"responseId":"cht000d6e99@dx19ebce1767eb87f702"}}
