{"type":"message","id":"7f6452aa","parentId":"c59d53e5","timestamp":"2026-06-12T17:29:34.150Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**v6.13 修复完成：**\n\n| # | 问题 | 根本原因 | 修复 |\n|---|------|----------|------|\n| 1 | 快门/光圈不加载 | `apiGet('/function')` 和 `loadShutter` 并行执行 | 嵌套到 `.then()` 内顺序执行 |\n| 2 | OSD 开关不工作 | 按钮更新函数没更新开关状态 | 添加 `sw.checked = enabled` |\n| 3 | WASM 状态错误 | 状态在登录开始设置，不是播放成功 | 在 `clickStartRealPlay` 成功回调设置 |\n| 4 | 降噪无提示 | `setNoiseReduce` 没有 showToast | 添加成功/失败提示 |\n| 5 | 设备名称显示型号 | 用了 `connected.model` | 改用 `connected.name` |"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":53062,"output":186,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53248,"cost":{"input":0.053062,"output":0.0005952,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.053657199999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781285365775,"responseId":"cht000d3caf@dx19ebce1abdeba5c342"}}
{"type":"message","id":"23e716bb","parentId":"7f6452aa","timestamp":"2026-06-12T17:32:26.541Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System (untrusted): [2026-06-13 01:29:11 GMT+8] Exec completed (vivid-bl, code 0) :: سɹ� [INFO] �汾: v6.13 [TEST] �л����豸����... [INFO] �豸����: 1 [DEBUG] ��������: <tr><td><span class=\"badge manual\">�ֶ�</span></td><td>240f9b764193</td><td>192.168.5.72</td><td>--</t…\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"33803\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-06-13 01:32 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n你又乱改\n1. 现在WASM的异步被改没了，连接的时候无法切换标签，一直卡在设备管理？\n2. 快速连接，显示没有上次连接的设备？那我之前连接的是什么？\n3. 设备管理连接，现在WASM连灰色框都没了\n退回上一次修改，备份后重新迭代，版本6.14"}],"timestamp":1781285546537}}
