{"type":"message","id":"f10410cc","parentId":"0cee79b8","timestamp":"2026-06-12T18:19:16.662Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"`allDevices` 在第 222 行声明。**问题是 `allDevices` 被多次重置**，可能导致快速连接时读取到空值。\n\n**根本问题：断开连接后调用 `refreshDevices`，在 API 响应之前 `allDevices` 被清空了？**\n\n检查断开连接后的 `refreshDevices` 调用："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8453ad8a4d09415baa828e1c","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":20,"offset":1400,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":129593,"output":125,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":129718,"cost":{"input":0.12959299999999999,"output":0.0004,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.129993}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781288346534,"responseId":"cht000dea50@dx19ebd0f30b7b91a742"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2177d2fa","parentId":"f10410cc","timestamp":"2026-06-12T18:19:16.672Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_8453ad8a4d09415baa828e1c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                if (window.connectedDevice && window.connectedDevice.ip === ip) {\r\n                    window.connectedDevice = null;\r\n                    addLog('info', '已清除连接设备状态');\r\n                }\r\n                if (window.updateDeviceStatus) window.updateDeviceStatus();\r\n                refreshDevices();\r\n                refreshPtzDeviceList();\r\n                refreshAdvancedDeviceSelectors();\r\n                var panel = document.getElementById('deviceInfoPanel');\r\n                if (panel) panel.style.display = 'none';\r\n            }).catch(function(e) {\r\n                showToast('error', '断开异常: ' + e.message);\r\n            });\r\n        }\r\n        function deleteDevice(identifier) {\r\n            if (!confirm('确定删除设备 ' + identifier + '？')) return;\r\n            apiDelete('/api/v1/devices/' + identifier).then(function() {\r\n                showToast('success', '设备已删除');\r\n                addLog('info', '设备已删除: ' + identifier);\r\n                refreshDevices();\r\n\n[1317 more lines in file. Use offset=1420 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781288356672}}
{"type":"message","id":"369c270f","parentId":"2177d2fa","timestamp":"2026-06-12T18:19:37.614Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"`refreshDevices()` 是异步调用，如果用户**在刷新完成前点击快速连接**，`allDevices` 可能还没更新。\n\n**但老板说\"断开连接再连接循环\"，说明 `allDevices` 应该已经加载过了。**\n\n**检查快速连接的 MAC 匹配问题：**\n\n断开连接后 `allDevices` 应该有设备。问题可能是：\n1. `lastConnectedMac` 格式不对\n2. `allDevices` 中的 MAC 格式不对\n\n添加调试日志："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_46b4b2a24bd446749b817b36","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    // 快速连接函数（连接上次设备）\n    window.quickConnect = function(checked) {\n        if (checked) {\n            if (window.connectedDevice && window.connectedDevice.ip) {\n                console.log('[QUICK] Already connected');\n                return;\n            }\n            \n            var lastMac = localStorage.getItem('lastConnectedMac');\n            console.log('[QUICK] lastMac:', lastMac, 'allDevices:', window.allDevices ? window.allDevices.length : 'undefined');\n            \n            if (lastMac && window.allDevices && window.allDevices.length > 0) {\n                // v6.16: MAC 格式统一（去除分隔符）\n                var normalizeMac = function(mac) {\n                    return (mac || '').replace(/[-:]/g, '').toLowerCase();\n                };\n                var targetMac = normalizeMac(lastMac);\n                console.log('[QUICK] targetMac:', targetMac);\n                console.log('[QUICK] allDevices[0].mac:', window.allDevices[0] ? window.allDevices[0].mac : 'N/A');\n                \n                var dev = window.allDevices.find(function(d) {\n                    return normalizeMac(d.mac) === targetMac;\n                });\n                \n                console.log('[QUICK] found dev:', dev ? dev.ip : 'null');\n                \n                if (dev && dev.ip) {\n                    if (window.connectDevice) {\n                        window.connectDevice(dev.ip);\n                    }\n                } else {\n                    showToast('warning', '上次设备不在列表中');\n                    document.getElementById('quickConnectSwitch').checked = false;\n                }\n            } else {\n                showToast('warning', lastMac ? '设备列表为空' : '无上次连接记录');\n                document.getElementById('quickConnectSwitch').checked = false;\n            }\n        } else {\n            if (window.connectedDevice && window.connectedDevice.ip) {\n                disconnectDevice(window.connectedDevice.ip);\n            }\n        }\n    };","oldText":"    // 快速连接函数（连接上次设备）\n    window.quickConnect = function(checked) {\n        if (checked) {\n            if (window.connectedDevice && window.connectedDevice.ip) {\n                console.log('[QUICK] Already connected');\n                return;\n            }\n            \n            var lastMac = localStorage.getItem('lastConnectedMac');\n            console.log('[QUICK] lastMac:', lastMac);\n            \n            if (lastMac) {\n                // v6.16: MAC 格式统一（去除分隔符）\n                var normalizeMac = function(mac) {\n                    return (mac || '').replace(/[-:]/g, '').toLowerCase();\n                };\n                var targetMac = normalizeMac(lastMac);\n                \n                var dev = (window.allDevices || []).find(function(d) {\n                    return normalizeMac(d.mac) === targetMac;\n                });\n                \n                if (dev && dev.ip) {\n                    console.log('[QUICK] Found device:', dev.ip);\n                    if (window.connectDevice) {\n                        window.connectDevice(dev.ip);\n                    }\n                } else {\n                    showToast('warning', '上次设备不在列表中');\n                    document.getElementById('quickConnectSwitch').checked = false;\n                }\n            } else {\n                showToast('warning', '无上次连接记录');\n                document.getElementById('quickConnectSwitch').checked = false;\n            }\n        } else {\n            if (window.connectedDevice && window.connectedDevice.ip) {\n                disconnectDevice(window.connectedDevice.ip);\n            }\n        }\n    };"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":129985,"output":962,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130947,"cost":{"input":0.129985,"output":0.0030784000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1330634}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781288356674,"responseId":"cht000db360@dx19ebd0f53cfb958232"}}
