{"type":"message","id":"afde644c","parentId":"0acb88af","timestamp":"2026-06-12T18:37:01.565Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**断开连接时没有清除 `lastConnectedMac`，这是正确的。**\n\n**问题：连接时保存的是 `dev.mac`，而 `dev` 来自 `allDevices`。检查 `dev.mac` 格式：**\n\nAPI `/api/v1/devices` 返回的 `mac` 是 `240f9b764193`（无分隔符）。\n\n**直接测试：模拟前端调用：**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-f9fa1ffecb6547afbebbf981478d617c","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n    <title>Test Quick Connect</title>\n    <script>\n        // 模拟 allDevices\n        window.allDevices = [\n            { mac: \"240f9b764193\", ip: \"192.168.5.72\", name: \"4k 32X DC\" }\n        ];\n        \n        // 模拟 localStorage\n        localStorage.setItem('lastConnectedMac', '240f9b764193');\n        \n        // 测试快速连接逻辑\n        function testQuickConnect() {\n            var lastMac = localStorage.getItem('lastConnectedMac');\n            console.log('[TEST] lastMac:', lastMac);\n            console.log('[TEST] allDevices:', window.allDevices.length);\n            \n            var normalizeMac = function(mac) {\n                return (mac || '').replace(/[-:]/g, '').toLowerCase();\n            };\n            var targetMac = normalizeMac(lastMac);\n            console.log('[TEST] targetMac:', targetMac);\n            \n            var dev = window.allDevices.find(function(d) {\n                return normalizeMac(d.mac) === targetMac;\n            });\n            \n            console.log('[TEST] found dev:', dev ? dev.ip : 'null');\n            \n            if (dev && dev.ip) {\n                console.log('[TEST] SUCCESS: would connect to', dev.ip);\n            } else {\n                console.log('[TEST] FAIL: device not found');\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 运行测试\n        testQuickConnect();\n    </script>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <h1>Test Quick Connect - Check Console</h1>\n</body>\n</html>","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\tests\\test_quickconnect.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":125794,"output":460,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126254,"cost":{"input":0.125794,"output":0.0014720000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.127266}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781289397827,"responseId":"cht000e73f1@dx19ebd1f38a6b893102"}}
