{"type":"message","id":"97a72d71","parentId":"cf20913b","timestamp":"2026-06-12T18:43:35.623Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System (untrusted): [2026-06-13 02:43:23 GMT+8] Exec completed (salty-or, code 0) :: [TEST] ����ҳ... [PASS] ��ҳ���سɹ� [INFO] �汾: v6.16 [TEST] �л����豸����... [INFO] �豸����: 1 [DEBUG] ��һ��: �ֶ�240f9b764193192.168.5.72192.168.5.14k 32X DCiDS-2DF8C832IXS-A���߶Ͽ���Ϣ�޸…\n\nAn async command you ran earlier has completed. The result is shown in the system messages above. Handle the result internally. Do not relay it to the user unless explicitly requested.\nCurrent time: Saturday, June 13th, 2026 - 02:43 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-06-12 18:43 UTC"}],"timestamp":1781289815615}}
