{"type":"message","id":"0f1a4122","parentId":"d21bd00c","timestamp":"2026-06-12T18:54:57.413Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"33948\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-06-13 02:54 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n你现在给我整理，每次运行程序，自动连接上一次的设备，应该怎么做最合适，是运行之后输出json文档，记录最近连接设备信息？还是使用什么方式？"}],"timestamp":1781290497404}}
{"type":"message","id":"a8e59cb1","parentId":"0f1a4122","timestamp":"2026-06-12T18:55:29.669Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到。分析最佳方案：\n\n## 自动重连方案对比\n\n| 方案 | 优点 | 缺点 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **前端 localStorage** | 简单、快速、无需网络请求 | 刷新页面后可用，但关闭浏览器/换设备丢失 |\n| **后端 registry.json** | 持久化、跨设备可用 | 需要网络请求，但已有 `active_device` 字段 |\n| **两者结合** | 最佳体验 | 需要同步 |\n\n## 推荐方案：后端 registry.json + 前端恢复\n\n**已有基础设施：**\n- `registry.json` 已有 `active_device` 字段\n- `/api/v1/ptz/connected` 已返回活跃设备信息（包含凭证）\n\n**当前问题：**\n- 前端 `localStorage.lastConnectedMac` 和后端 `registry.json` 不同步\n- `quickConnect` 用 localStorage，但断开后设备信息可能不一致\n\n**最佳方案：**\n\n```\n启动流程：\n1. 前端调用 GET /api/v1/ptz/connected\n2. 如果返回 connected=true + device 信息：\n   - 直接恢复 window.connectedDevice\n   - 触发 WASM 登录\n3. 如果返回 connected=false：\n   - 检查 registry.json 的 active_device\n   - 如果有 active_device，尝试自动连接\n\n断开连接时：\n1. 后端清除 active_device 或标记为 inactive\n2. 前端清除 localStorage.lastConnectedMac\n```\n\n**需要修改吗？** 当前方案已经基本正确，只需：\n1. 断开时**不清除** `active_device`（保持记录）\n2. 前端 `localStorage` 作为缓存，优先用后端状态\n\n是否需要我按这个方案修改？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":145480,"output":386,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":145866,"cost":{"input":0.14548,"output":0.0012352,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1467152}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781290497414,"responseId":"cht000dfd9a@dx19ebd30341cba5a412"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c9642cc8","parentId":"a8e59cb1","timestamp":"2026-06-12T18:57:14.506Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"33951\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-06-13 02:57 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n如果返回 connected=false，提示无上次连接设备，请重新执行发现、初始化流程\n断开连接，你清除了活跃状态，那重启PC，下次打开程序，又要重新执行发现？我需要是记录上一次连接，并且自动连接"}],"timestamp":1781290634499}}
{"type":"message","id":"8ae72e8e","parentId":"c9642cc8","timestamp":"2026-06-12T18:57:24.488Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到。方案确定：\n\n**需求：**\n1. 程序启动自动连接上次设备\n2. 断开连接**不清除**活跃记录\n3. 如果无上次设备，提示执行发现流程\n\n**实现：**\n\n```\n启动时：\n- GET /api/v1/ptz/connected\n- 有设备 → 自动连接\n- 无设备 → 提示\"无上次连接设备，请执行发现\"\n\n断开时：\n- 清除前端 connectedDevice\n- 后端 active_device 保留（不清除）\n```\n\n**修改：**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ad5021751b8c4eba9dcab1c1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\core\\ptz_manager.py","offset":1670,"limit":40}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":146073,"output":166,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":146239,"cost":{"input":0.14607299999999998,"output":0.0005312,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1466042}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781290634507,"responseId":"cht000de28c@dx19ebd3219dcb958232"}}
