{"type":"message","id":"20c23ea2","parentId":"b54ac132","timestamp":"2026-06-12T19:31:20.990Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**v6.18 测试通过。**\n\n**清理总结：**\n\n| 删除项 | 原因 |\n|--------|------|\n| `localStorage.lastConnectedMac` | 多余，后端已有 `registry.json` |\n| `refreshDevices` 中的 auto-connect 逻辑 | 与 `restoreConnectionState` 重复 |\n| `quickConnect` 中的 MAC 匹配逻辑 | 简化为直接调用后端 API |\n\n**现在的流程：**\n\n```\n启动 → restoreConnectionState() → GET /api/v1/ptz/connected → 有设备则自动连接\n快速连接 → GET /api/v1/ptz/connected → 有设备则连接\n```"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":53557,"output":145,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53702,"cost":{"input":0.053557,"output":0.00046400000000000006,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.054021}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781292675553,"responseId":"cht000d015b@dx19ebd513377b958232"}}
{"type":"message","id":"10833704","parentId":"20c23ea2","timestamp":"2026-06-12T20:07:51.719Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"33998\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-06-13 04:07 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n复盘，更新记忆"}],"timestamp":1781294871715}}
{"type":"message","id":"c99fa0df","parentId":"10833704","timestamp":"2026-06-12T20:08:32.188Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到。复盘 v6.18 清理。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-29c8842a04074d4ea8a2e67d2f4124b7","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 复盘 - v6.18 代码清理\n\n**日期**: 2026-06-13 04:07\n**版本**: v6.18\n\n## 问题根源\n\n过度开发导致状态混乱：\n- `localStorage.lastConnectedMac` + `allDevices` + `refreshDevices` 形成复杂依赖链\n- 多处代码修改 `allDevices`，导致\"设备列表为空\"误报\n- `refreshDevices` 中的 auto-connect 与 `restoreConnectionState` 功能重复\n\n## 清理内容\n\n| 删除项 | 位置 | 原因 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| `localStorage.lastConnectedMac` | 多处 | 后端 `registry.json` 已记录 |\n| auto-connect 逻辑块 | `refreshDevices()` | 与 `restoreConnectionState` 重复 |\n| MAC 匹配逻辑 | `quickConnect()` | 简化为直接调用后端 API |\n\n## 简化后的流程\n\n```\n【启动】\ninit() → restoreConnectionState() → GET /api/v1/ptz/connected\n→ 有设备 → 自动连接 ISAPI + WASM\n→ 无设备 → 提示\"执行发现流程\"\n\n【快速连接】\n点击开关 → GET /api/v1/ptz/connected → 有设备则连接\n\n【断开】\n点击断开 → ISAPI logout + WASM logout → 清除前端状态\n→ 后端 registry.json 保留设备信息（不清除）\n```\n\n## 教训\n\n1. **单一数据源原则**：后端已有 `registry.json`，前端不应再用 localStorage 存同一数据\n2. **避免重复逻辑**：auto-connect 应只在一处实现\n3. **简化优于缓存**：直接调用 API 比 complex 本地缓存逻辑更可靠\n4. **全局变量谨慎**：`allDevices` 被多处覆盖是隐患\n\n## 后端修复\n\n`get_connected_device()` 读凭证路径错误：\n- 原：`info.get('credentials', {}).get('username')`\n- 改：`creds.get('username') or info.get('username')`\n\n凭证在 `info.json` 根级别，不是嵌套对象。\n\n## 文件变更\n\n- `src/web/index.html` - 删除 localStorage/auto-connect 逻辑\n- `src/core/ptz_manager.py` - 修复凭证读取路径\n\n## 备份位置\n\n`backup_20260613_032900/`","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\.learnings\\LEARNINGS.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":51156,"output":568,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51724,"cost":{"input":0.051156,"output":0.0018176000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0529736}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781294871720,"responseId":"cht000d5ae4@dx19ebd730fd2b91a742"}}
