{"type":"message","id":"a4460433","parentId":"996def47","timestamp":"2026-06-12T20:08:45.187Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_90eecfff5b3c49c59a02dad7","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 教训记录\n\n**日期**: 2026-06-13\n\n## LRN-20260613-001: 单一数据源原则\n\n**问题**: 前端 `localStorage.lastConnectedMac` 与后端 `registry.json` 存储相同数据，导致状态不同步。\n\n**教训**: \n- 后端已有持久化存储时，前端不应再创建本地副本\n- 直接调用 API 获取状态，比本地缓存 + 同步逻辑更简单可靠\n\n## LRN-20260613-002: 全局变量覆盖问题\n\n**问题**: `allDevices` 被多处代码修改（`refreshDevices`, `loadWasmDevices`），导致值被意外覆盖。\n\n**教训**:\n- 全局变量应只在一处赋值\n- 如果多处需要修改，考虑封装为函数或使用事件机制\n\n## LRN-20260613-003: JSON 结构假设错误\n\n**问题**: `get_connected_device()` 假设凭证在 `info.credentials` 对象中，实际在根级别。\n\n**教训**:\n- 读取 JSON 前先确认实际结构\n- 添加兼容逻辑：`info.get('credentials', {}).get('x') or info.get('x')`\n\n## LRN-20260613-004: 过度开发\n\n**问题**: 为了\"优化体验\"添加了 `localStorage` 缓存、auto-connect 逻辑，反而增加复杂度和 bug。\n\n**教训**:\n- 先实现最简方案，确认可用后再考虑优化\n- 每增加一层抽象，就增加一层出错可能\n- Karpathy 原则：不写超出需求的功能","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\.learnings\\ERRORS.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":54476,"output":393,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54869,"cost":{"input":0.054476,"output":0.0012576000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.055733599999999994}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781294912202,"responseId":"cht000da93b@dx19ebd735855ba60352"}}
