{"type":"message","id":"b445a8e8","parentId":"d7228c52","timestamp":"2026-06-12T20:08:52.552Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"..."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ce23f351fdad443da4b69205","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"# 心跳与任务状态\n\n**最后更新**: 2026-06-13 04:07\n**状态**: v6.18 清理完成\n**工作空间**: C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\n\n### v6.18 清理内容\n| # | 删除项 | 原因 |\n|---|--------|------|\n| 1 | localStorage.lastConnectedMac | 后端已有 registry.json |\n| 2 | refreshDevices 中的 auto-connect | 与 restoreConnectionState 重复 |\n| 3 | quickConnect 中的 MAC 匹配 | 简化为调用后端 API |\n\n### 简化后的流程\n```\n启动 → GET /api/v1/ptz/connected → 有设备则自动连接\n快速连接 → GET /api/v1/ptz/connected → 有设备则连接\n断开 → ISAPI/WASM logout → 清除前端状态（后端保留设备信息）\n```\n\n### 数据存储\n- registry.json → active_device（后端持久化）\n- devices/{mac}/info.json → 设备详情 + 凭证\n\n### 备份位置\n- backup_20260613_032900/","oldText":"# 心跳与任务状态\n\n**最后更新**: 2026-06-13 02:20\n**状态**: v6.16 调试中\n**工作空间**: C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\n\n### v6.16 待解决问题\n| # | 问题 | 状态 |\n|---|------|------|\n| 1 | 快速连接循环弹窗 | 调试中 - 添加日志检查 MAC 匹配 |\n| 2 | 断开连接后 WASM 仍播放 | 已修复 - 调用 updateWasmStatus('disconnected') |\n\n### 调试命令\n```javascript\n// 浏览器控制台执行\nlocalStorage.getItem('lastConnectedMac')\n```\n\n### 备份位置\n- backup_20260613_021200/ - v6.16 备份"}],"path":"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":52380,"output":526,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52906,"cost":{"input":0.052379999999999996,"output":0.0016832000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0540632}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781294925205,"responseId":"cht000e5650@dx19ebd73894bb893102"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ce963bb9","parentId":"b445a8e8","timestamp":"2026-06-12T20:08:52.566Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ce23f351fdad443da4b69205","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"edit\",\n  \"error\": \"Could not find the exact text in C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/HEARTBEAT.md. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\\nCurrent file contents:\\n# 心跳与任务状态\\n\\n**最后更新**: 2026-06-13 02:45\\n**状态**: v6.17 快速连接循环弹窗修复完成\\n**工作空间**: C:\\\\Users\\\\admin\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\dev-factory\\\\astrohub\\n\\n### v6.17 修复内容\\n| # | 问题 | 状态 |\\n|---|------|------|\\n| 1 | 快速连接循环弹窗 | ✅ 已修复 - 添加 `_quickConnectSkipNext` 标志防止程序化修改触发循环 |\\n| 2 | 断开连接后 WASM 仍播放 | ✅ 已修复 - 调用 updateWasmStatus('disconnected') |\\n\\n### 修复原理\\n- 问题：快速连接失败时设置 `checked = false` 触发 `onchange` 事件，导致循环调用\\n- 解决：在程序化修改 checkbox 前设置 `_quickConnectSkipNext = true`，跳过下一次 onchange\\n\\n### 备份位置\\n- `backup_20260613_021200/` - v6.16 备份\\n\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"edit","error":"Could not find the exact text in C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/HEARTBEAT.md. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\nCurrent file contents:\n# 心跳与任务状态\n\n**最后更新**: 2026-06-13 02:45\n**状态**: v6.17 快速连接循环弹窗修复完成\n**工作空间**: C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\n\n### v6.17 修复内容\n| # | 问题 | 状态 |\n|---|------|------|\n| 1 | 快速连接循环弹窗 | ✅ 已修复 - 添加 `_quickConnectSkipNext` 标志防止程序化修改触发循环 |\n| 2 | 断开连接后 WASM 仍播放 | ✅ 已修复 - 调用 updateWasmStatus('disconnected') |\n\n### 修复原理\n- 问题：快速连接失败时设置 `checked = false` 触发 `onchange` 事件，导致循环调用\n- 解决：在程序化修改 checkbox 前设置 `_quickConnectSkipNext = true`，跳过下一次 onchange\n\n### 备份位置\n- `backup_20260613_021200/` - v6.16 备份\n"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781294932566}}
