{"type":"message","id":"536f94d5","parentId":"bba0371e","timestamp":"2026-06-12T20:09:06.833Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**复盘完成。**\n\n**总结：**\n\n| 项目 | 内容 |\n|------|------|\n| **问题** | 过度开发导致状态混乱（localStorage + allDevices + auto-connect 多重依赖） |\n| **清理** | 删除 localStorage 缓存、重复 auto-connect、复杂 MAC 匹配逻辑 |\n| **简化** | 统一用后端 API `/api/v1/ptz/connected` 获取上次设备 |\n| **修复** | `get_connected_device()` 凭证读取路径错误 |\n| **教训** | 单一数据源、避免全局变量覆盖、不过度开发 |"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":56136,"output":130,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56266,"cost":{"input":0.056136,"output":0.00041600000000000003,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.056552}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781294941655,"responseId":"cht000d67b0@dx19ebd73c7efb9ca102"}}
